# Smart Waste Management System

A web-based volunteer-driven waste management system for reporting waste, assigning volunteer cleanup tasks, tracking request status, and encouraging responsible waste disposal.

## Tech Stack

- Frontend: React.js
- Backend: Laravel (PHP)
- Database: MySQL
- Rendering Method: Client-Side Rendering (CSR)
- Version Control: GitHub

## Main Features

- Landing page
- User registration and login
- Role-based dashboard
- Waste report / pickup request
- Volunteer task assignment
- Waste verification
- Eco-point reward system
- Admin reporting dashboard

